# ❌⭕ Tic-Tac-Toe Game

## 👨‍💻 Author

Shubham Rajput

## 📌 Description

This is a simple Tic-Tac-Toe game developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It supports two-player gameplay with automatic winner detection and game reset features.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 🎮 Features

- Two-player game (X and O)
- Turn-based gameplay
- Winner announcement
- Draw detection
- Reset and New Game options
- Interactive UI

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open `tick.html` in your browser
2. Start playing the game

## ⭐ Project Goal

To build a simple interactive game using JavaScript and improve logic building skills.
